#To be completed

# Install Instructions
#---------------------
A) Gmail Configuration:
	1) Create a rule to archive received fax emails to a particular label (Ex. Fax)
	2) Create a rule to archive Faxator receipt emails to a particular label (Ex. Fax)

B) Program Installation:
	1) Install and configure "lpr" with a working printer.
	2) Configure parameters in the "settings.conf" file 
	3) Create needed directories (Paths section)
	4) Copy the files in a choosen directory
	5) Eventually verify apparmor settings
	6) Create a cron job that launchs the script on periodic interval
	6) Enjoy!
